OOC: RYO, the engine technology is MILLIONS of years apart!  Remember in 
Season 3 of Beast Wars?  They had a lot of trouble getting Teletran 1 to work 
because it was old technology.  The same thing would go for the engines.  
Shomin's trying his best, but he has a real life outside this RPG, that is 
more important.

:::Starscream:::

::He cursed under his breath::
Starscream: Well, how do we get out of this mess?
